actions.description: Obtain messages from the email account that this connection is authorized to access.

propertyDefinitionSteps.description: Specify the emails that you want to obtain.
propertyDefinitionSteps.name: Obtain Messages from Email

unseenOnly.label: consumer
unseenOnly.labelHint: If true, only fetch unseen messages.

delay.label: consumer,scheduler
delay.labelHint: Time interval between polls for emails.

maxResults.label: consumer
maxResults.labelHint: Maximum number of emails to return (use -1 to fetch all of them).

actions.name: Receive Email

description: Receive email messages from an imap or pop3 account.
name: Receive Email (imap or pop3)

protocol.labelHint: The type of the email server, ie. imap or pop3

host.description: The hostname of the email server.
host.label: common

port.description: The port of the email server.
port.label: common

username.label: common,security
username.labelHint: Specify a user name for authentication of the email service url, if required.

password.label: common,security
password.labelHint: Specify a password for authentication of the email service, if required.

secure.label: security
secure.labelHint: Specify whether this is an ssl enabled connection

serverCertificate.description: If the SSL email server is internal and possesses a self-signed certificate then enable SSL by adding the certificate here.
serverCertificate.label: common,security
